data.description: 167 Foxwood Circle Saint Marys, GA 31558.The home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a 2-car garage. Newer roof with architectural shingles. Tile through main areas and LVP in the owner's suite. Carpet in the bedrooms. Newer A/C compressor. Large fenced in lot, NO HOAs, NO city taxes, No water or sewer bills. It has its own well and septic and NO flood insurance required. Located close to the Crooked River State Park, boat ramp, Naval Base and shopping. Owners have recently replaced the kitchen appliances within the last year and a half. The washer/dryer is only 3 months old. The well pump is brand new. Water softener is installed and works as well. Kitchen counters, farm sink and faucet are new. Real wood cabinets in the kitchen. Walk in closet in owner's suite. Screened patio with tile floors that are newer. Fireplace has been inspected recently (November) and septic tank was pumped out last year. Ceiling fans and all light fixtures are newer. Owner's suite shower is less than 6 months old with a double vanity. Toilets are about a year old. Nest thermostat and a camera and doorbell. Spacious driveway. Newer aerator. Beautiful oak in the back yard.
